{"tid":1765502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察招募新口號 : 「如果您想保護香港這個家」　","createTime":"2019-12-02T02:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T12:32:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":410,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"76e06f4f27230301bbd8a205a29f900d2f024a47","tid":1765502,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/76720781_10156792325607544_7405353504769835008_o_yIQZH_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F76720781_10156792325607544_7405353504769835008_o_yIQZH_1200x0.jpg&h=a653dde1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據星島日報報道，在抗爭運動下，以往「爭崩頭」的鐵飯碗政府職位，包括政務主任職系，申請人數減少約 3000 人，即是跌兩成，平均 267 人爭一個位。另外，警察招募以新口號作招徠，包括「如果您想保護香港這個家」&mdash; 榮譽、心繫社會，使命等。<br />\n<br />\n星島日報報道，今年度申請政務主任職系人數相較 2018/19 年度跌兩成，有 1萬 2000 人。二級行政主任職系申請人數比上年度大減 4000 人，共 1 萬 9000 人，跌幅 18%。報道指，AO 及 EO 的申請人數創了「佔中運動」後的新低，跟政府形象長期低落有關。<br />\n<br />\n警隊今個財政年度目標是招募 1815 名警務人員，當中見習督察 195 名，警員 1620 名，另外輔警警員 320 名。6月以來，警民衝突持續升級，警察不時舉行的 4 點鐘記者亦不見改善到崩緊的警民關係，警方在招募時，亦側重迎難而上、忠誠、肩負使命等口號及理念。四款新的口號分別是：「如果您想保護香港這個家」&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;榮譽、心繫社會，使命；「如果您想守護香港」 &mdash; 撲滅罪行、忠誠、肩負使命；「如果您想維護法紀」 &mdash; 執法、繩之於法、滅罪；「如果您想並肩前行」 &mdash; 堅定不移、勇毅、迎難而上。<br />\n<br />\n除了招新人，警方亦計劃招募大約 1000 名退休警務人員「回巢」幫手處理警務工作，首批將於本月重返警隊，當中部分曾是總督察級別，部分會加入刑事或軍裝。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B8%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%8B%9B%E5%8B%9F%E6%96%B0%E5%8F%A3%E8%99%9F-%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%82%A8%E6%83%B3%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E5%AE%B6-%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-%E6%8A%95%E8%80%83-ao-eo-%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E6%80%A5%E8%B7%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%258B%259F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%2599%259F-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259E%259C%25E6%2582%25A8%25E6%2583%25B3%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B3%25B6-%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%2580%2583-ao-eo-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25B7%258C%2F&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0Y429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=701ceee9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%258B%259F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%2599%259F-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259E%259C%25E6%2582%25A8%25E6%2583%25B3%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B3%25B6-%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%2580%2583-ao-eo-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25B7%258C%2F&h=c68f25c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B8%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%8B%9B%E5%8B%9F%E6%96%B0%E5%8F%A3%E8%99%9F-%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%82%A8%E6%83%B3%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E5%AE%B6-%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-%E6%8A%95%E8%80%83-ao-eo-%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E6%80%A5%E8%B7%8C/</a>"},{"pid":"974b0a0ad74425dbacd9f32fa2ab085ca7b884cb","tid":1765502,"uid":154054,"like":569,"dislike":3,"score":566,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:20:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果您想保護香港這個家，就不要做警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"37440aa12de5ae64582c6ed078a05b1d896c8b86","tid":1765502,"uid":34075,"like":100,"dislike":3,"score":97,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:21:06.000Z","msg":"用呢